snippet.title: From The Rain Game Trailer
snippet.description:
From The Rain is a single player survival horror game. Reboot the generator, lock all entrances, and defend yourself from the entities that lurk in the rain. Survive each hour and wait for help to arrive!

Steam Link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2232290/From_The_Rain/

I am 17 years old and have always dreamed of being able to post a game on Steam. And now, it is finally official!

#horrorgaming #indiegame #madewithunity #scarygaming #gamedev #fromtherain #fnaf
